naveed-portfolio/
├── index.html                     ← clean HTML only
├── package.json                   ← Vite
├── vite.config.js
├── .env.example                   ← AI config template
├── src/
│   ├── main.js                    ← entry point
│   ├── config.js                  ← reads VITE_* env vars
│   ├── styles/
│   │   ├── base.css               ← variables, themes, cursor, transitions
│   │   ├── layout.css             ← nav, hero, sections, footer, responsive
│   │   ├── components.css         ← cards, pills, buttons, form, experience
│   │   └── chat.css               ← floating chat widget
│   ├── modules/
│   │   ├── theme.js               ← dark/light toggle + localStorage
│   │   ├── cursor.js              ← custom cursor
│   │   ├── constellation.js       ← star canvas (theme-aware)
│   │   ├── scroll.js              ← reveal animations + active nav
│   │   └── contact.js             ← Web3Forms submission
│   └── ai/
│       ├── index.js               ← bootstrap — picks provider, mounts widget
│       ├── chat-widget.js         ← floating chat UI (self-contained DOM)
│       ├── context.js             ← structured portfolio data for AI prompts
│       └── providers/
│           ├── base.js            ← abstract AIProvider interface
│           ├── openai.js          ← direct OpenAI API (with streaming)
│           └── langchain.js       ← LangChain backend proxy